Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Two Much With Kajol And Twinkle Official Trailer
Starring Kajol, Twinkle Khanna, Salman Khan, Aamir Khan, Govinda, Chunky Panday, Vicky Kaushal, Kriti Sanon, Varun Dhawan, Alia Bhatt, Janhvi Kapoor, Karan Johar.
Created by Banijay Asia

Official Release Date September 25, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Kajol and Twinkle are serving up a talk show with a twist - equal parts masti, magic and maybe even some manic energy. Expect wild hot takes, controversial opinions and the kind of honesty that makes you say, ‚ÄúDude, same!‚Äù 
Joining them are their friends who just happen to be some of the biggest stars in the country (and even the world). With eight unique pairs gracing the couch this season, the conversations jump from filmy nostalgia to family drama, love, paparazzi, fame and everything in between.
What sets it apart is the unapologetic female gaze - a perspective that‚Äôs funny, sharp, and not afraid to hold up a mirror to society. One moment you‚Äôre laughing embarrassingly loudly, the next you‚Äôre caught off guard by an insight that might make you question your own life choices. 
Basically, it‚Äôs a vibe: two women side-by-side, yapping with their friends. Think of it as the fun table at the party, sunny, chatty, and just unhinged enough to keep you hooked.

snippet.title: Wakka Lagdo Sansar - bekcha - Jodi No.1 Title Song [Lyrical Video]
snippet.description:
#wakkalagdosansar #Jodino1 #bekcha 
Wakka Lagdo Sansar is the original soundtrack for an amazing web series Jodi No. 1 made with love, soul and perseverance by brilliant human beings with big dreams. When you have the time and mind, go catch it here:

The first episode: https://youtu.be/lCakw0IyOt4
Full Channel : https://www.youtube.com/@UC3uDjw2Sg4EgPfZeAR_Q2rQ 

I would like to pay respects to the brave fighters, martyrs of the current movement in Nepal. The whole nation mourns this massive loss and is forever indebted to all of  you.  I am sending out prayers to the bereaved family and friends.

I sit here many miles away wondering what went wrong, why this had to happen and if the unbearable losses had to happen. I fail to make sense of most of it. There is but a glimmer of hope with this morning's announcement. But I still have fear in the back of my mind that things may turn out worse. I hope I am wrong and I hope better days are on the way. Thank you,  Generation Z, all the mighty warriors from September 8, everyone who took part in this revolution. 


Also, I'm not sure right now is a space for me to describe the song. To put it briefly, this expresses frustration and annoyance at how at times the endless torment life can feel like. If this makes you feel worse, maybe come back to the song some other time. The release was planned a week back,  and things went seriously south, but maybe now we shall all slowly resume. Shall come back with more... The official video will be out soon.

Wishing all of you strength, peace and love. Please keep up the kindness, camaraderie and  the big little things. I hope to be able to help in some way.

Audio Credits:
(Produced, Mixed and Mastered by) https://www.instagram.com/begendra_official
https://www.instagram.com/anmolz_music
Guitars: https://www.instagram.com/bishalchhetriguitar/
Sansic Productions

i'm in instagram sometimes - https://www.instagram.com/b3kcha
and mail me here, if you feel it should get to me: songsbybekcha@gmail.com

snippet.title: Anuv Jain - Arz Kiya Hai (Official Lyrical Video)
snippet.description:
For centuries, poets have given voice to the human heart, shaping the language of love. #ArzKiyaHai carries that legacy forward as an intimate tribute rooted in India‚Äôs poetic tradition, embracing the unguarded honesty of speaking your heart. At its helm is India‚Äôs most popular independent artist, Anuv Jain, pairing delicate guitar work with achingly tender vocals that distill this very emotion into melody. Joining him is Indian electronic duo Lost Stories working their magic on the production of the track as well as performing on the harmonium.

Listen to Arz Kiya Hai: https://UMGI.lnk.to/ArzKiyaHai_CSBS3

CREDITS

Written, Composed, and Performed By: Anuv Jain
Producer: Lost Stories
Additional Production and Additional Vocals: Sarthak Kalyani
Backing Vocals: Solomon Konwar Rengme, Anahita Singh
Acoustic Guitars, Electric Guitars, Charango, Bass Guitars: Keba Jeremiah

What is Roblox?
Roblox is an online platform and game creation system where users can play, create, and share 3D games and experiences. It features a vast library of user-generated games, supports social interaction, and uses a virtual currency called Robux for in-game purchases. Popular among kids and teens, it‚Äôs accessible on multiple devices and emphasizes creativity and community.
